        <h2>12. Stakeholder Impact Analysis</h2>
        <div class="analysis-box">
            <h3>Multi-stakeholder Perspectives</h3>
            <p>The childcare crisis affects various stakeholders differently:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Families:</li>
